snippet.title: Crashlands - Announcement Trailer (June 2015)
snippet.description:
Go to http://www.crashlands.net to get a launchday email and Wishlist our steampage (http://store.steampowered.com/app/391730)! Launches on Jan 21, 2016 for iOS, Android, and Steam!

Follow the three Butterscotch brothers on twitter @bscotchshenani

To listent to those sweet Crashlands tunes,  check out the preview over on Fat Bard's bandcamp: http://fatbard.bandcamp.com/album/crashlands-preview-jams

BscotchID: https://id.bscotch.net/about.html
Podcast: https://forums.bscotch.net/podcast/
Forums: https://forums.bscotch.net
Blog: http://www.butterscotch-shenanigans.com
